{"role": "SAFETY", "text": "Safety: The most frequent adverse reactions reported in the INBRIJA® clinical studies were cough (15.6%), fall (8.7%), upper respiratory tract infection (5.8%), dyskinesia (5.7%) and sputum discoloured (2.8%). Serious adverse reactions of allergic oedema have been reported with levodopa medicinal products but not in clinical studies with INBRIJA®. Gastrointestinal haemorrhage has been reported with levodopa medicinal products and was observed once in INBRIJA® clinical studies.1", "n": 1, "coverage": 0.2, "window_months": 18, "first_seen": "2024-01", "source_id": "asset_ce98a97e20bb", "pattern_id": "uk_email_safety_8caf08d5"}
